citations:
    citation-agot-catelyn-iv:
        source: source-agot
        properties:
            locator: "Catelyn IV"
            accessed: "2026-03-06"
        notes: "Catelyn and Ser Rodrik travel by galley (the Storm Dancer, captained by Moreo Tumitis of Tyrosh) to King's Landing. Catelyn's hands are injured from the assassin's blade. Littlefinger's history revealed: ward of Catelyn's father at Riverrun, dueled Brandon Stark for Catelyn's hand at age 15, was scarred and sent away. Catelyn arrives at King's Landing; Littlefinger's men (City Watch) escort her to him. Varys and Littlefinger reveal the assassin's dagger belonged to Tyrion Lannister."
